Democratic Senator Barack Obama was given certain arrangements to reach the agreement, particularly the one that would allow the owners to keep their home and the one on the salary of the leaders of the surviving companies by the state.
" When taxpayers are asked to take extraordinary measures because of the irresponsibility of some, they should not be congratulated.
